      • log

        public static void log(Object instance,
       Object... params)
        This is a stack trace method, if you want a normal log use print(Object...) method. This method print the instance, instance class, parameters and stack trace from Thread in a json format.
        Parameters:
        instance - the instance, normally use this reference.
        params - anything you want see besides the instance and stack trace, this support a variable number of parameters.
